  12:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****                         ##### How to use this driver #####
  13:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  14:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****   [..]
  15:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****   The DMA Extension HAL driver can be used as follows:
  16:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****    (+) Configure the DMAMUX Synchronization Block using HAL_DMAEx_ConfigMuxSync function.
  17:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****    (+) Configure the DMAMUX Request Generator Block using HAL_DMAEx_ConfigMuxRequestGenerator funct
  18:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****        Functions HAL_DMAEx_EnableMuxRequestGenerator and HAL_DMAEx_DisableMuxRequestGenerator can t
  19:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****        to respectively enable/disable the request generator.
  20:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c **** 
  21:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****    (+) To handle the DMAMUX Interrupts, the function  HAL_DMAEx_MUX_IRQHandler should be called fro
  22:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****        the DMAMUX IRQ handler i.e DMAMUX1_OVR_IRQHandler.
  23:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****        As only one interrupt line is available for all DMAMUX channels and request generators , HAL
  24:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****        called with, as parameter, the appropriate DMA handle as many as used DMAs in the user proje
  25:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****       (exception done if a given DMA is not using the DMAMUX SYNC block neither a request generator
  26:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c **** 
  27:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_dma_ex.c ****   @endverbatim
